==Spanish==
===Etymology===
Vulgar Latin ''*accordare'', from [[cor]] ‘heart’.

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/akoɾˈdaɾ/}}

===Verb===
'''acordar'''
# ''(transitive)'' to [[decide]], to [[arrange]]
# ''(intransitive)'' to [[agree]]
# ''(reflexive)'' to reach agreement
# ''(reflexive)'' to [[remember]], [[recall]]

